# Fixtures layout

All test fixture **assets** live under repo-root [`ops/fixtures/`](ops/fixtures/). Resolve paths via [`ops/lib/fixturepaths.ts`](ops/lib/fixturepaths.ts).

`zss/feature/` and `cafe/public/` must not import `ops/fixtures` or host test/parity/archive code.

## Required

| Domain | Path under `ops/fixtures/` |
|--------|------------------------|
| Lang parity | `lang/parity/` + `manifest.json` |
| Lang integration sources | `lang/scripts/` |
| Lang integration goldens | `lang/integration/` |
| Book corpus | `lang/coolregionsbow/` |
| Memory WASM | `memory/wasm/` |
| Synth | `synth/wasm/`, `synth/daisy/`, `synth/maxi/` |
| Wanix WASI | `wanix/` (Go `wasip1` fixtures in `wanix/<name>/`; `yarn task run wanix:wasm:build`) |
| Dev-served static | `public/` (served at `/fixtures/` in dev only) |
| Offline renders | `renders/` (daisy offline wav/json/txt; served at `/renders/` in dev only) |
| Book templates | `content/templates/`; build output `content/dist/` |
| Books (npm) | `books/` |
| Generated training | `generated/training/` |
| ZZT corpus | `zzt/corpus/` (`zss/` committed; `archives/`, `extracted/`, `screenshots/` gitignored) |

```typescript
// ✅ GOOD
import { LANG_PARITY_DIR } from 'ops/lib/fixturepaths'
path.join(LANG_PARITY_DIR, `${id}.zss`)

// ❌ BAD — co-located fixture trees
path.join(__dirname, '__fixtures__/parity')

// ❌ BAD — legacy paths
'ops/fixtures/wanix/hello/main.go'
'src/fixtures/example-coolregionsbow.book.json'
```

## Generated vs committed

- Regenerate `ops/fixtures/generated/training/` via existing tasks/scripts.
- Lang/memory/synth goldens: regen via parity/regen tests — do not hand-edit unless fixing the generator.

## Ops layout

| Kind | Location |
|------|----------|
| Fixture path constants | `ops/lib/fixturepaths.ts` |
| ZZT corpus walk + OOP compile | `ops/lib/content/zztcorpuswalk.ts` |
| ZZT corpus layout / element extract | `ops/lib/content/zztcorpus.ts` |
| ZZT profanity scan/sanitize | `ops/lib/content/zztcorpussanitize.ts` |
| Daisy parity / bench | `ops/lib/daisy-parity/` |
| Task spawn / Jest helpers | `tasks/shellutil.ts` |
| Task Playwright / parity glue | `tasks/lib/` |
| Legacy Tone/Maxi synth | `ops/archive/synth/` |
| Jest test helpers | `ops/lib/test/` |

See [`ops/fixtures/README.md`](ops/fixtures/README.md) for regen task ids.
